com.hazelcast.internal.util

Class RuntimeAvailableProcessors

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.internal.util.RuntimeAvailableProcessors

  • public final class RuntimeAvailableProcessors
extends Object
    Utility class to access Runtime.availableProcessors() and optionally override its return value.

    This class makes the number of available processors configurable for the sake of testing. override(int) and resetOverride() should only be used for testing purposes.
